Arrived in paradise. This is @idle.awhile and it is a Five-Star villa located on Jamaica’s famous Seven Mile Beach! There are 6 oceanfront retreats to choose from and it feels so secluded and like you have a piece of Jamaica all to yourself! This is one of those gems that you have to truly experience for yourself. When we arrived I felt like I was entering somewhere that felt like a James Bond retreat. The villas are luxurious with boutique touches and also can come with a private chef! We just loved everything about it and this will be a place we can see ourselves coming back over and over again. Would you stay here?!
.
.

Kruger National Park is truly wonderful, welcome to the wild South Africa 🇿🇦 

We stayed 6 nights in this paradise ⬇️

🦒 @kapamaprivategamereserve is a private luxury safari game lodge and the biggest private reserve offering accommodation with spa & game viewing of the big 5. It’s nestled between Blyde River Canyon & Kruger Park South Africa
It offers a total of 5 luxurious accommodations types. We stayed at River Lodge and Southern Camp 💦🛖

🐆 @safari.moon.lodge is a luxury boutique hotel in the Hoedspruit Wildlife Estate. Only 6 stylish suites for the moment so it’s really private, we stayed in the delicious Porcupine Suite. This luxury accommodation has a safari access to the Kruger National Park and can arrange game drives at your request. 🦓🍇
Tom Cruise stayed there during part of the filming of the latest “Mission Impossible”, which was shot in the same area.
